        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> You don't have Honolulu branches created in https://gerrit.onap.org/r/c/ci-management/+/120040/, so why the cherry-pick?\n\nOkay. I was just modifying the existing csit files in the ci-management. I thought that we were running CSIT for both master and the current release. Does this mean, previously CI didn't have a CSIT job for the branches",
